column16: Mike Napoli called out on strikes.
Dustin Pedroia grounds out sharply, third baseman Manny Machado to first baseman Chris Davis.
Shane Victorino homers (5) on a line drive to right field.
Lorenzo Cain grounds into a force out, second baseman Brian Roberts to shortstop J.   Hardy.   Eric Hosmer out at 2nd.
Jairo Asencio intentionally walks Edwin Encarnacion.
Jose Bautista doubles (20) on a line drive to left fielder Nate McLouth.   Emilio Bonifacio scores.    Jose Reyes to 3rd.
Jose Reyes singles on a ground ball to right fielder Nick Markakis.   Munenori Kawasaki to 2nd.
Munenori Kawasaki grounds into a force out, pitcher Jairo Asencio to shortstop J.   Hardy.   Mark DeRosa out at 2nd.    Munenori Kawasaki to 1st.
